1. copy mvn.cmd to mvn.bat
2. mvn clean archetype:create-from-project -DpackageName=org.study.archetype
3. make sure the .m2 folder exists
4. edit file:target\generated-sources\archetype\src\main\resources\archetype-resources\pom.xml
5. edit file:target\generated-sources\archetype\src\main\resources\archetype-resources\readme
6. mvn clean install under target\generated-sources\archetype